text: Krasny Vostok () is a rural locality (a village) in Bakhmutsky Selsoviet, Kuyurgazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 66 as of 2010. There is 1 street. == Geography == It is located 12 km from Yermolayevo, 6 km from Bakhmut. == References == Category:Rural localities in Kuyurgazinsky District
title: Krasny Vostok, Kuyurgazinsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
